# Local dev: `npx convex dev` usually writes VITE_CONVEX_URL into .env.local for you.

# Production builds (e.g. GitHub Actions): set VITE_CONVEX_URL to your *production* Convex URL.

# GitHub Pages project site (not user site root): set at build time, e.g.
#   VITE_BASE_PATH=/m-othello/
# Must include leading and trailing slashes for non-root hosting.
